    "content": "<p>If the magnitude of the coefficient of x<sup>7</sup> in the expansion of $${\\left( {a{x^2} + {1 \\over {bx}}} \\right)^8}$$, where a, b are positive numbers, is equal to the magnitude of the coefficient of x<sup>7</sup> in the expansion of $${\\left( {ax + {1 \\over {b{x^2}}}} \\right)^8}$$, then a and b are connected by the relation</p>",
