    "content": "<p>If $\\left(1+x-2 x^2\\right)^6=1+a_1 x+a_2 x^2+\\ldots+a_{12} x^{12}$, then the value of $a_2+a_4+a_6+\\ldots+a_{12}$ is</p>",
